    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 8pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .ConsPlusNonformat {font-family: 'Courier New'; font-size: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'Times New Roman';}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 53px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Фуқаролик ишлари бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#2}Ариза берилган фуқаролик суди номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\"> судига</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Фуқаро: </span><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#4}Боланинг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Боланинг Ф.И.О.си</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Телефон: </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Боланинг телефон рақами</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Электрон почта манзили: </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Боланинг электрон манзили</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 3=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Даъво мазмуни:</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">АРИЗА</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">(тўлиқ муомалага лаёқатли деб топиш ҳақида)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Мен, </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Боланинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Боланинг туғилган вақти</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> туғилганман, бугунги кунда меҳнат шартномаси асосида </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Боланинг иш жойи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ишлайман. Мен васийлик ва ҳомийлик органига мени тўлиқ муомалага лаёқатли деб топиш ҳақида ариза берган эдим, лекин мазкур орган аризамни рад этди. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Шунга кўра, мени меҳнат шартномаси асосида ишлаётганимни инобатга олган ҳолда тўлиқ муомалага лаёқатли шахс деб топишингизни сўрайман.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\"> Илова:</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">1. Aриза нусхаcи.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">2. Меҳнат шартномаси нусхаси.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">3. Ишга қабул қилиш ҳақидаги буйруқ нусхаси.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">4. Туғилганлик ҳақида гувоҳнома нусхаси. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Фуқаро </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Боланинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 377.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Ариза берилган сана</span></p>\n</div></div>",
